    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and retaining its original aesthetic integrity. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a commitment to meticulous stewardship. Mechanically peerless and visually arresting, this offering represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle of uncompromising quality.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
